Table.Name: DdsUpgradeLog
Table.com:Description: This table stores DDS version upgrade log. It is used by Radix Manager. The table is created by creation script (0.sql)

Table.Name: DdsOption
Table.com:Description: This table stores information about database configuration (is partitioning in use, etc). It is created by create script (0.sql), filled by manager and used by manager and at runtime for preprocessing.
